name: FIRE HORSE 丙午
description: FIRE HORSE 丙午 -Chinese New Year 2026- In the year of Fire Horse, according to Chinese calender, those born in the year are believed to possess courage, transformation, and powerful movement. The Fire Horse appears only once in 60 years. The last one was in 1966, and it changed the world. It is the rarest and most transformative energy of the Chinese zodiac. “Fire horse, an energy to awaken passion and purpose”
